&lt;p&gt;Newham Perinatal Mental health team, has an opportunity to expand as part of the Long Term Plan for Mental health.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nursing is an essential part of the service and this new role will help the service develop new ways of supporting women and their families at this important time in their life. We are looking for someone who has a keen interest in this area and has innovative and creative ideas, to help contribute to our expansion.&lt;/p&gt;
